{"tid":1060272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C.朗令全球瘋狂！里奧費迪南：他是活著的上帝","createTime":"2019-03-13T16:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T16:22:54.000Z","uid":14719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf9eec803b0c653078f4ff0f48280e32ee91935","tid":1060272,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uTndyTe90pY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuTndyTe90pY&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=a952c704\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uTndyTe90pY</a><br />\n<br />\n上週的歐聯比賽，阿積士和曼聯分別在作客完成了逆轉。而到了這個星期，祖記回到主場完成了大逆轉，C.朗拿度的帽子戲法幫助球隊進軍八強。葡萄牙巨星頭頂腳踢大發神威，兩粒頭槌更是極其精彩。賽後在社交媒體上，也引發了稱讚C.朗拿度的狂潮。<br />\n<br />\n談到C.朗本場比賽的表現，曼聯名宿里奧費迪南稱讚道：「他就是活著的足球上帝！」里奧費迪南還發Twitter表示：「哈哈哈哈哈哈這個傢伙&hellip;&hellip;永遠不要懷疑他！」<br />\n<br />\n  （華迪維亞）<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20190313/0/4/2/C-朗令全球瘋狂里奧費迪南-他是活著的上帝-9890035.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F0%2F4%2F2%2FC-%E6%9C%97%E4%BB%A4%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E9%87%8C%E5%A5%A7%E8%B2%BB%E8%BF%AA%E5%8D%97-%E4%BB%96%E6%98%AF%E6%B4%BB%E8%91%97%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%9D-9890035.html&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=c81e3f3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20190313/0/4/2/C-朗令全球瘋狂里奧費迪南-他是活著的上帝-9890035.html</a>"}]}